{"word":"βραδύνω","slug":"βραδύνω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βραδύνω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βραδύς'><el>βραδύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to make slow, delay</i>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be delayed</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to be long, to loiter, delay</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>: so in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}